article_node.title: Martha Stewart Meets Wishbone Kitchen's Meredith Hayden After Years of Cross-Generational Comparison
article_node.summary: Meredith Hayden, the TikTok cooking influencer behind Wishbone Kitchen, recently met her idol Martha Stewart at a celebration in East Hampton, sparking a social‑media exchange that highlighted Hayden’s admiration for both Stewart and Ina Garten.  The 29‑year‑old has built a career as a private chef, cookbook author and brand partner, drawing inspiration from the lifestyle moguls while carving out her own niche as a “Walmart Martha Stewart.”  Hayden’s upcoming cookbook, The Wishbone Kitchen Cookbook, showcases her signature summer‑focused recipes and entertaining tips, and she continues to grow her audience with videos, collaborations and a growing business empire.  The meeting underscored her journey from culinary student to influencer‑chef, emphasizing her belief that modeling one’s career after successful mentors can lead to personal and professional fulfillment.
